'''{{ill|Nomisukune Shrine|ja|野見宿禰神社}}''' (Nomisukune Jinja) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}} enshrining {{ill|Nomisukune|ja|野見宿禰}}, who is regarded as the progenitor of {{ill|sumo|ja|相撲}} and the ancestor of the {{ill|Haji clan|ja|土師氏}}. There are shrines with the same name in {{ill|Hyōgo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県}} ({{ill|Tatsuno City|ja|たつの市}}) and in {{ill|Tokyo|ja|東京都}} ({{ill|Sumida Ward|ja|墨田区}}). * {{ill|Nomisukune Shrine (Sumida Ward)|ja|野見宿禰神社 (墨田区)}} * {{ill|Nomisukune Shrine (Tatsuno City)|ja|野見宿禰神社 (たつの市)}}
